{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because maybe-- there were-- there were a lot of camps in this area because this was in the-- in the Silesian part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and he said to me, this pill-- is-- this is the only pill I have left, and these-- these are hard to come by and I'm gonna give you this pill.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this will make you completely healthy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was power of suggestion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted so hard to get well that I-- I recouped from it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I also had like a little looking glass, a mirror.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know where I got it, but I used to keep it under my bed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I used to look at it, and I must have been delirious from the temperature, you know, the high temperature, and it seemed to me like my face is getting smaller every time I looked at it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was very fortunate because maybe I-- I heal fast and that kept me alive, because they constantly transported people out of the camp-- dead bodies, not people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because this camp did not have a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the smell was always prevalent no matter what, because the conditions and the sanitary facilities were very minimum, and limited, and-- so-- but it was like, not-- not-- not enough to live and not enough to die.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This camp we had to evacuate because I think that we-- they were-- the Russian-- were moving closer, and they were always concerned to leave live prisoners wherever they, so they always shipped us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- from there, we went on a death march from Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was cold, was winter time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were marching-- took us quite a while to get there-- I don't if it was a week, 10 days, or two weeks.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
